title: Aetna
description: Aetna, a prominent player in the healthcare insurance industry, is recognized for its vibrant and diverse brand palette. The brand colors range from the energetic magenta (#D20962) and lively orange (#F47721) to the refreshing green (#7AC143). Complementing these are the serene shades of teal (#00A78E), cyan (#00BCE4), and a regal purple (#7D3F98). These colors, documented and verified by brandingguide.app, reflect Aetna's commitment to a dynamic and trustworthy image.
